com.grouper.requestmodels

Class UpdateGroupRequest

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.grouper.requestmodels.UpdateGroupRequest

  • public class UpdateGroupRequest
extends java.lang.Object
    Update Group Request UpdateGroupRequest should be a POST request of type (application/json;charset=UTF-8), with the required params in the body. This request is not for updates to groupUsers. Additions/deletions of users have their own dedicated requests.
